Isra Hirsi (amụrụ na Febụwarị 22, 2003) bụ onye America na-agba mbọ maka ọdịmma gburugburu ebe obibi
O guzobere ma rụọ ọrụ dị ka onye isi nchịkwa nke U.S
Hirsi tolitere na Minneapolis, Minnesota, ọ bụkwa nwa nwanyị nke nwanyị omeiwu U.S
aha ya bụ Ilhan Omar na Ahmed Abdisalan Hirsi

Mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na abụọ, ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị sonyere na-eme ngagharị iwe maka ikpe ziri ezi maka Jamar Clark na Mall of America. Hirsi gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Minneapolis South, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na 2021. Ọ malitere itinye aka na mmegide ihu igwe mgbe ọ sonyeere klọb gburugburu ebe obibi nke ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya n'afọ mbụ ya.
Hirsi haziri nhazi nke ọtụtụ narị ọgbaghara ụmụ akwụkwọ na mba United States na Maachị 15 na Mee 3, 2019. O so guzobe U.S

Youth Climate Strike, aka America nke mgbanwe ihu igwe nke ndị ntorobịa zuru ụwa ọnụ, na Jenụwarị 2019. Ọ na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye isi nchịkwa nke otu a. N'afọ 2019, o ritere ihe nrite Brower Youth Award. N'otu afọ ahụ, Hirsi natara Voice of the Future Award. N'afọ 2020, e denyere aha Hirsi na ndepụta "Future 40" nke BET.

A kọrọ na Hirsi na-aga Barnard College nke Mahadum Columbia ka ọ na-erule oge mgbụsị akwụkwọ 2021. N'ọnwa Mee 2021, Hirsi nwetara mmeghachi omume site n'aka ndị na-achọghị mgbanwe mgbe ọ gbasịrị hama na mma na profaịlụ Twitter ya.
N'afọ 2020, a kpọrọ aha ya na Fortune's 40 Under 40 Government and Politics list.
